\": 0.00028189984655915427, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"State-owned utility\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"EDF\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"guarantees\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"origin\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"six wind\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"two solar production sites\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CARBON OFFSETS To make up for the some of the emissions that are not being avoided, notably spectator air travel, Paris 2024 has purchased 1.3 million carbon credits.\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"CARBON OFFSETS\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"the emissions\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"notably spectator air travel\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"1.3 million carbon credits\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each credit represents one ton of emissions reduced or removed elsewhere - from projects protecting biodiversity-rich forests in Kenya and Guatemala and improving access to clean cooking in Kenya, Nigeria and the Democratic Republic of Congo.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3339, \"end\": 3344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 5.8658286392706305e-12, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 3349, \"end\": 3358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"score\": 0.9999791904752487, \"rank\