{\"ngram\": \"four forestry projects\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3536}, {\"ngram\": \"14,500 tons\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"greenhouse gases\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although carbon credits can channel money to climate-friendly projects, often in the Global South, some credit-generating projects have been scrutinised over false claims about the benefits they deliver.\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"carbon credits\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3617}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"climate-friendly projects\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3664}, {\"ngram\": \"the Global South\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3691}, {\"ngram\": \"some credit-generating projects\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"false claims\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"the benefits\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 had positioned itself as the first climate-positive Games in reference to plans to remove, reduce or offset more emissions than it generates.\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3804}, {\"ngram\": \"the first climate-positive Games\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"reference\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\": 3889}, {\"ngram\": \"more emissions\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has since dropped such claims, pledging instead to reduce its climate impact and support climate projects.\", \"from\": 3952, \"to\": 4061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such claims\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 3984}, {\"ngram\": \"its climate impact and support climate projects\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS Olympics E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice Need help?\"